item.title: I need help over all
item.dc:creator: @xone xone
item.description:
@xone wrote:

I can’t help you on the leveling now… But I probably will later.

To make people admins on Fr33sc4p3, you first need to create your character. Make it with any username and password, and then get out of it. Go into your fr33sc4p3 pkz folder and go into characters. Find the character that you want to make mod/admin/owner and open it. It should say something like CharacterRights = 0 or PlayerRights = 0 or something like that. Change the 0 to a 1, 2 or 3. 1 for mod, 2 for admin and 3 for owner. If my memory serves me correctly, 4 is banned.

Hope I helped.

Seth
